
### Basic agent test
POST http://localhost:8088/responses HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"message": "Hello! What can you help me with?",
	"agentid": "basic",
	"conversation_id": "",
	"parameters": {
		"user_id": "JDOE",
		"username": "John Doe"
	}
}


